    +image(4, imgpath, " Improved inducible oscillatory circuit at induction point T=55", 100)
    :markdown-it(html)
    
        ## Molecular dynamics

        One crucial part of the oscillatory system was the protein AiiA, which is a lactonase that degrades AHLs. To determine the affinity of the lactonase, docking was performed using [molecular dynamics](https://2020.igem.org/Team:Stockholm/Model#MolecularDynamics), and the energies used to determine kinetic constants to the different AHLs used.

